\sum_{k=1}^{n+1} \binom {n+1} {k} = \sum_{k=1}^{n} \binom {n+1} {k} + \binom{n+1}{n+1} = (n+1)\sum_{k=1}^{n}\binom {n} {k} + 1 = (n+1)(2^n-1)+1 = n2^n-n+2^n-1+1 = 2^n(n+1)-n
